title: Goran Todorčev
text:
Goran Todorčev () (born 21 January 1984 in <a href="Negotino">Negotino</a>) is a <a href="Macedonia%20%28country%29">Macedonian</a> retired <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
Club career.
He rejoined <a href="FK%20Rabotni%C4%8Dki">Rabotnički</a> after playing for the Croatian club <a href="NK%20Inter%20Zapre%C5%A1i%C4%87">Inter Zaprešić</a>.
International career.
Todorčev was called up to the Macedonian national team for the first time for a friendly against Albania on 17 November 2010 but he was forced to withdraw because of an injury.
